Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: #ComradeKamala has called for Abolishing ICE and closing every ICE detention facility. She supports free healthcare for illegal immigrants and has promised to give illegals mass amnesty and citizenship, which will obliterate Social Security and Medicare. Defund the PoliceKamala is always going to have open borders. If Comrade Harris has the chance, she will allow 100 million illegal aliens into our country.
